title: Cinema 4D R16 Win - Mac Hybrid Installer ISO
description:
This is another Hybrid Installer for Maxon Cinema4d R16: It Includes all maxon software in the installer though I include all serials for this installer.

 I have not fully tested this Cinema4d Version yet So im not 100% that every single thing is working as I was in my R15 upload. Though it comes from the same source So I imagine everything Is working.

As before you will need winemu which is the only clean windows iso mounter I know about. Or similar mounting software for mac. This will install on either.
Don't forget whenever you open Cinema4d for the first time you will need to goto edi
